{"tid":613932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南生圍橫水渡遭縱火　負責人：原因唔敢講","createTime":"2018-04-02T05:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T08:46:11.000Z","uid":74778,"like":140,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"4609a380956a96be720f72759ef6404fbb11c404","tid":613932,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"11:30】元朗區議員鄺俊宇今早到達南生圍縱火現場視察，他表示今次火警好大可能係人為，背後目的他不會推測，但認為警方要盡快緝兇，政府亦要加強南生圍的保育，不要讓自然的環境任由人為破壞，應該將南生圍留給下一代好好珍惜。 <br />\n<br />\n【11:00】渡頭負責人譚先生對事件似乎一言難盡，據他表示，昨晚11時許，工人將船隻泊回碼頭後收工，至今早6時許返回開工時，嚇見船隻起火立即報警及一度救火，而焚毀船隻可戴客6人，價值10多萬港元，連同今日的人工開支以及營業額，譚損失慘重。對於今次遭人縱火，與早前南生圍的婚紗橋被拆，以及之前兩宗縱火案是否有關，譚指不敢揣測，「話佢有又唔係，無又唔係，話佢影響生態，呢度搞吓你，嗰度搞吓你，都唔出奇喎...呢啲都係交畀警方處理」。記者又問他可有見過可疑人出沒，譚不欲多提，指「自己係退休人士，經營呢度，其他嘅嘢唔會理，就算知我都係睇唔到㗎啦，好難講㗎，呢度地方咁大，發生乜嘢事都無人知㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n【09:25】4男1女探員到現場蒐證，並向橫水渡碼頭的負責人錄取口供，由於現場裝有閉路電視，警方翻查片段追查。 <br />\n<br />\n-------------------------- <br />\n元朗南生圍又發生火警，早上6時22分，南生圍盡頭的橫水渡碼頭突然起火，冒出大量濃煙，船主發現立即報警。由於碼頭是用木板搭建，火勢迅速蔓延。消防員接報趕至，開喉灌救，約10分鐘後將火救熄，碼頭的斜台燒毀，綁在旁邊的一艘船隻亦告燒毀沉沒，消防調查後，相信起火原因有可疑，交警方調查。 <br />\n<br />\n該碼頭於清晨6時至晚上11時開始運作，接載市民橫過山貝河，每程六港元。由於碼頭設有正、副碼頭兩處，而是次燒毀部分接近副碼頭，故仍有正碼頭可以給居民登船上落，故橫水渡的服務未受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n有「香港人的後花園」及「雀鳥天堂」稱譽的元朗南生圍，於上月22日、13及12日先後發生火警，大片山草及蕉樹燒毀，其中兩宗火警有可疑。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135155_03c0b1962e9d4ab1431bcae7f6028a27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135155_03c0b1962e9d4ab1431bcae7f6028a27.png&h=d9117e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135156_e5fcf7785502bfa8d3dae40a0108014d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135156_e5fcf7785502bfa8d3dae40a0108014d.png&h=513d2944&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135156_d08d76aaec2a6bcd932f142f2852ca68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135156_d08d76aaec2a6bcd932f142f2852ca68.png&h=1328bd7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135157_f60544ad278050253f10455d807613c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135157_f60544ad278050253f10455d807613c6.png&h=23c075a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135158_1a3352df4d4c23fa43d7791e3a9b1df7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135158_1a3352df4d4c23fa43d7791e3a9b1df7.png&h=620cfc90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135159_1a3352df4d4c23fa43d7791e3a9b1df7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135159_1a3352df4d4c23fa43d7791e3a9b1df7.png&h=8a1b6c31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135159_8eb38da7ba42733fc2e07b02411f94f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135159_8eb38da7ba42733fc2e07b02411f94f3.png&h=fa0ac8da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135200_42d6ea5978d9d6463747213f1ddf79e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135200_42d6ea5978d9d6463747213f1ddf79e0.png&h=e985809d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135201_3ed7bc7a4fb791fe1c91a086663f57e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F135201_3ed7bc7a4fb791fe1c91a086663f57e4.png&h=a0607b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/135212_75f3a5919593a91c435fa33ae261432a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa